    if (category === 'All') return true;

      case 'Diamonds': return item.category.diamonds !== null;
      case 'Jewelry Store': return item.category.jewelryStore !== null;
      case 'Watches': return item.category.watches !== null || item.category.watchesLocal !== null;

              <div className="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                <div className="bg-purple-50 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-purple-100">
                  <p className="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style={{ color: BRAND.purple }}>Filtered Keywords</p>
                  <p className="text-xl font-bold" style={{ color: BRAND.dark }}>{filteredStats.totalKeywords.toLocaleString()}</p>
                </div>
                <div className="bg-purple-50 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-purple-100">
                  <p className="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style={{ color: BRAND.purple }}>Filtered Volume</p>
                  <p className="text-xl font-bold" style={{ color: BRAND.dark }}>{filteredStats.totalVolume.toLocaleString()}</p>
                </div>
                <div className="bg-purple-50 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-purple-100">
                  <p className="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style={{ color: BRAND.purple }}>Genesis #1</p>
                  <p className="text-xl font-bold" style={{ color: BRAND.success }}>{filteredStats.rankingOne}</p>
                </div>
                <div className="bg-purple-50 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-purple-100">
                  <p className="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style={{ color: BRAND.purple }}>Avg Ranking</p>
                  <p className="text-xl font-bold" style={{ color: BRAND.dark }}>{filteredStats.avgRanking}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            )}

            {/* Keywords Table */}
            <div>
              <h3 className="text-lg font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style={{ color: BRAND.dark }}>
                <Search className="w-5 h-5" style={{ color: BRAND.purple }} />
                All Keywords
                <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full ml-1" style={{ backgroundColor: BRAND.purple }}></span>
              </h3>
              
              {/* Sort Options */}
              <div className="flex gap-2 mb-4">
                <button
                  onClick={() => handleSort('volume')}
                  className={`px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium ${sortConfig.key === 'volume' ? 'text-white' : ''}`}
                  style={{ 
                    backgroundColor: sortConfig.key === 'volume' ? BRAND.purple : BRAND.light,
                    color: sortConfig.key === 'volume' ? 'white' : BRAND.dark
                  }}
                >
                  Volume {sortConfig.key === 'volume' && (sortConfig.direction === 'desc' ? '' : '')}
                </button>
                <button
                  onClick={() => handleSort('genesis')}
                  className={`px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium ${sortConfig.key === 'genesis' ? 'text-white' : ''}`}
                  style={{ 
                    backgroundColor: sortConfig.key === 'genesis' ? BRAND.purple : BRAND.light,
                    color: sortConfig.key === 'genesis' ? 'white' : BRAND.dark
                  }}
                >
                  Genesis Rank {sortConfig.key === 'genesis' && (sortConfig.direction === 'desc' ? '' : '')}
                </button>
                <button
                  onClick={() => handleSort('keyword')}
                  className={`px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium ${sortConfig.key === 'keyword' ? 'text-white' : ''}`}
                  style={{ 
                    backgroundColor: sortConfig.key === 'keyword' ? BRAND.purple : BRAND.light,
                    color: sortConfig.key === 'keyword' ? 'white' : BRAND.dark
                  }}
                >
                  Keyword {sortConfig.key === 'keyword' && (sortConfig.direction === 'desc' ? '' : '')}
                </button>
              </div>

              <KeywordsTable 
                data={processedData} 
                page={currentPage} 
                setPage={setCurrentPage}
                showAllCompetitors={false}
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        ) : (
          <LocationView location={activeTab} />
        )}
      </main>

      {/* Footer */}
      <footer className="bg-white border-t border-gray-100 mt-8">
        <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 text-center">
          <p className="text-sm" style={{ color: BRAND.darkLight }}>
            Genesis Diamonds Local Keyword Research Dashboard
            <span className="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full mx-2" style={{ backgroundColor: BRAND.purple }}></span>
            {RAW_DATA.length.toLocaleString()} Keywords Analyzed
          </p>
        </div>
      </footer>

      {/* Custom CSS */}
      <style>{`
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');
        * { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; height: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: ${BRAND.light}; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: ${BRAND.purple}40; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: ${BRAND.purple}60; }
      `}</style>
    </div>
  );
}
